<!-- ── CEO statement ── -->
<div class="ceo-band">
  <div class="ceo-inner">
    <div class="ceo-photo">
      <img src="~/images/careers-ceo-richard-han.webp" alt="Richard Han, Chief Executive Officer" />
    </div>
    <div class="ceo-text">
      <div class="ceo-from">A message from our CEO</div>
      <p class="ceo-para">
        Hana serves a global market covering a diverse range of industries.
        Our leading edge capabilities play an important role for the
        automotive, mobile communications, IoT, medical, computing,
        industrial &amp; consumer markets. Whilst we continually invest in
        leading edge technologies — the real key to our success are our team
        of highly skilled professionals in many disciplines that support our
        growth. We have over 10,000 staff but we pride ourselves in
        maintaining a family management style with a strong focus on the
        wellbeing of our employees and developing them to their full potential.
      </p>
      <p class="ceo-italic">If you think you can contribute and have the ability — why not consider joining the 'Hana Family' to see how far you can go in playing your part in the fast growing world of microelectronics?</p>
      <div class="ceo-attrib">
        <strong>Richard Han</strong>
        <span>CEO of Hana Group</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

